{"tid":1511753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一可以制裁黑狗，救番義士既方法","createTime":"2019-08-27T15:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:08:35.000Z","uid":149652,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d855619b1924ef5628f5167c0a0b6966ae02fdfa","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"就係一齊推條仆街八婆林奠落台！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衣家黑狗可以咁肆無忌大，完全唔怕獨立調查，完全係因為班黑狗係跟條八婆指示做野，個八婆都講明唔成立獨立調查委員會，保護佢地。<br />\n即係有林奠一日，班黑狗都唔洗負任何刑責<br />\n<br />\n當林奠衣家落台，尼個時勢一定有更多真正為香港既人出來參選，班選委都一定會傾向投佢地票，一定唔會再傾向選個共匪指定既賤種做特首。所以習種先唔比個八婆衣家辭職。<br />\n<br />\n衣家仲講下個都一樣既，咩林奠留係到對香港好既，一係就三毛，一係就比三毛洗曬腦 無獨立思考既人"},{"pid":"5524ebe0c48c092f4b453c957c535dc1440968fe","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2899ca5f9469312ace1ad2d96c2c391e6736b594","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0f83e7f3ef24b746e1748aa5ad94b86ad97779df","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5d84b27574e3e1437a1853d65d4f21de36cf7362","tid":1511753,"uid":109221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"奶媽只係傀儡"},{"pid":"d6fa59dd90f0e2723859ec69566d55adc11fc5eb","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4c0d35d0e208d8890d6223e6b9c2073f3054da3a","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"412aad086d44b790a7010586692bd2e26f5199d9","tid":1511753,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a86f587f3b39dde35f4a2bd7b20e27ce1301f34a","tid":1511753,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d84b27574e3e1437a